model.productcontainer

Class ProductGroup

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.common.Model
      • model.productcontainer.ProductContainer
        • model.productcontainer.ProductGroup
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<IModel>, IModel

    public class ProductGroup
extends ProductContainer
    The ProductGroup class encapsulates all the funtions and data associated with a "ProductGroup". It extends the ProductContainer class which contains getters and setters for the various datas.
